Halalan
Version 0.1.4
http://sourceforge.net/projects/halalan
Copyright (C) 2006-2007 UP Linux Users' Group


REQUIREMENTS:

--- PHP 5.x.x
--- GD 2.x.x
--- PostgreSQL 7.4.x
--- Webserver with the rewrite module turned on
--- Javascript-enabled web browser


TESTED:

--- PHP 5.1.4, 5.2.0
--- GD 2.0.33, 2.0.34
--- PostgreSQL 7.4.12, 8.1.5
--- Apache 2.2.2, 2.2.4
--- Firefox 1.5.0.x, 2.0.0.x


INSTALLATION:

--- Unpack the distribution
--- Create the database from db/halalan.sql
--- Add an admin account; use sha1 for its password
--- Change configuration in config.php and conf/db.php if necessary
--- Create writable directories: templates/.compiled, includes/images/captcha, files
--- That's all